    "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n100% of the 587 tests from the command line in #1688  succeed in iteration 1, ~20% of the tests fail in iteration 2+ consistently\r\n[nonreentrant.txt](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/files/5960772/nonreentrant.txt)\r\n\r\n**Steps/Code to reproduce bug**\r\nSwitch to the #1688  branch commit https://github.com/gerashegalov/spark-rapids/commit/3dc64b9b5aac9c4d75fa4a743763d96e995b61f8\r\nand run \r\n```bash\r\nIT_MAX_ITERATIONS=-1 SPARK_HOME=~/spark-311 SPARK_SUBMIT_FLAGS='--master local-cluster[1,20,20000]' \\\r\nintegration_tests/run_pyspark_from_build.sh -k 'test_select'\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nTest should deterministically succeed regardless how often rerun\r\n\r\n**Environment details (please complete the following information)**\r\nlocal, local-cluster, standalone \r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nNone",
